<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٠ - <span class="c2">(١٦٣٧)</span> قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/16352">أَبُو إِسْحَاقَ إِبْرَاهِيمُ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/9913">الْحَسَنُ بْنُ بِشْرٍ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">سُفْيَانُ </a>بِهَذَا الْحَدِيثِ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>